I"8Q<p>Good typography is invisible, enabling users to have a seamless experience while theyâ€™re using Firefox products.</p>

<h2 id="typefaces">Typefaces</h2>

<p>In Firefox products we use the standard typeface for each platform.</p>

<form><div data-tabs="">
  <input type="radio" name="ptabs" id="platform-win" checked="checked" />
  <label for="platform-win">Windows</label>
  <div data-tab="" class="grid-2">

      <p><img src="../images/typography/typography-segoe.svg" alt="List of Segoe UI weights used in Firefox products" /></p>

      <p><a href="https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/windows/uwp/design/downloads/#fonts">Segoe UI</a> is the typeface used on the Windows platform.</p>

    </div>

  <input type="radio" name="ptabs" id="platform-mac-os" />
  <label for="platform-mac-os">macOS</label>
  <div data-tab="" class="grid-2">

      <p><img src="../images/typography/typography-san-francisco.svg" alt="List of San Francisco weights used in Firefox products" /></p>

      <p><a href="https://developer.apple.com/fonts/">San Francisco</a> is the standard typeface on Apple macOS.</p>

    </div>

  <input type="radio" name="ptabs" id="platform-ubuntu" />
  <label for="platform-ubuntu">Linux</label>
  <div data-tab="" class="grid-2">

      <p><img src="../images/typography/typography-ubuntu.svg" alt="List of Ubuntu weights used in Firefox products" /></p>

      <p><a href="http://font.ubuntu.com/">Ubuntu</a> is the typeface used in Ubuntu, the most common Linux distro.</p>
    </div>

  <input type="radio" name="ptabs" id="platform-web" />
  <label for="platform-web">Web</label>
  <div data-tab="" class="grid-2">

      <p><img src="../images/typography/typography-fira-sans.svg" alt="List of Fira Sans weights used in Firefox products" /></p>

      <div>
        <p><a href="https://mozilla.github.io/Fira/">Fira Sans</a> is the typeface used in Firefox web products.</p>

        <p>Despite <strong>Open Sans</strong> being used on some Mozilla web properties, it is currently not recommended for Firefox products.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

  <input type="radio" name="ptabs" id="platform-android" />
  <label for="platform-android">Android</label>
  <div data-tab="" class="grid-2">

      <p><img src="../images/typography/typography-roboto.svg" alt="List of Roboto weights used in Firefox products" /></p>

      <p><a href="https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Roboto">Roboto</a> is the standard typeface on Android. <strong>Noto</strong> is the standard Android typeface for all languages not covered by Roboto.</p>

    </div>

  <input type="radio" name="ptabs" id="platform-iOS" />
  <label for="platform-iOS">iOS</label>
  <div data-tab="" class="grid-2">

      <p><img src="../images/typography/typography-san-francisco.svg" alt="List of San Francisco weights used in Firefox products" /></p>

      <p><a href="https://developer.apple.com/fonts/">San Francisco</a> is the standard typeface on the Apple iOS.</p>

    </div>
</div>
</form>

